---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Travel Within | You're not stuck. You're repeating."
  description="Systemic coaching to see and interrupt the patterns that keep running your life."
>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-tw-black text-white pt-36 pb-24 md:pt-44 md:pb-32">
      <div class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 hidden lg:block w-1/2 opacity-45">
        <img src="/images/hero.jpg" alt="Travel Within" class="h-full w-full object-cover object-[60%_30%]" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-tw-black via-tw-black/70 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-end">
        <div class="lg:col-span-8">
          <p class="mb-8 inline-flex bg-tw-yellow text-tw-black px-5 py-2 rounded-full text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.22em] font-medium">
            Pattern interruption work
          </p>
          <h1 class="font-highlight text-6xl md:text-8xl lg:text-[7.5rem] leading-[0.92] tracking-tighter font-medium max-w-5xl">
            You're not stuck.<br />
            You're repeating.<br />
            <span class="italic text-tw-yellow">And that can change.</span>
          </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-4 lg:pb-4">
          <div class="border-l border-white/25 pl-6 space-y-5 text-xl md:text-2xl font-light leading-relaxed text-white/85">
            <p>You’re not broken.</p>
            <p>You’re repeating something you haven’t seen yet.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/work-with-me" class="mt-10 inline-flex bg-tw-yellow text-tw-black px-8 py-5 rounded-full items-center gap-3 hover:bg-white transition-colors group font-medium">
            <span class="text-base tracking-wide uppercase">Book Your Session</span>
            <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-5 h-5 stroke-[1.5] group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white py-24 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-12">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-14">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <p class="text-tw-green uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-sm font-medium mb-5">You’ve done the work</p>
          <h2 class="font-highlight text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-none tracking-tighter text-tw-black">
            And yet, the same situations keep coming back.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8 text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-snug font-light text-tw-black">
          <p>You’ve reflected. You’ve tried to evolve. You’ve tried to “fix” things.</p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium">
            <p class="bg-tw-gray-100 p-6 rounded-[2rem]">Different job.<br /><span class="text-tw-green">Same tension.</span></p>
            <p class="bg-tw-gray-100 p-6 rounded-[2rem]">Different people.<br /><span class="text-tw-green">Same dynamics.</span></p>
            <p class="bg-tw-gray-100 p-6 rounded-[2rem]">Different effort.<br /><span class="text-tw-green">Same result.</span></p>
          </div>
          <p class="font-highlight italic text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight text-tw-purple">
            At some point, you start wondering: “Is it me?”
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-tw-gray-100 py-24 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-12">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-14 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-6 space-y-8 text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-snug font-light text-tw-black">
          <p><strong class="font-medium">No.</strong> It’s not just you.</p>
          <p>But it’s not random either.</p>
          <p>What you’re experiencing is not bad luck. And it’s not a lack of effort.</p>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-tw-yellow pl-6 space-y-3 text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium">
            <p>You’re not stuck because you’re weak.</p>
            <p>You’re not stuck because you’re lazy.</p>
            <p>You’re not stuck because you “haven’t done enough work”.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-6 bg-tw-black text-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[3rem]">
          <h2 class="font-highlight text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-none tracking-tighter mb-8">
            You’re caught in patterns that didn’t start with you.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-snug font-light text-white/85 mb-8">
            But you’re the one repeating them.
          </p>
          <p class="text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-tight font-highlight italic text-tw-yellow">
            Because what you don’t see, runs the show.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white py-24 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-12">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mb-16">
          <p class="text-tw-green uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-sm font-medium mb-5">What this work is</p>
          <h2 class="font-highlight text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-none tracking-tighter text-tw-black mb-8">
            I don’t help you “feel better”.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-snug font-light text-tw-black">
            I help you see what’s actually running your life. I help you understand the cycles that keep on repeating and interrupt them at the root.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <article class="bg-tw-green text-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] min-h-[320px] flex flex-col justify-between">
            <span class="text-tw-yellow uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-sm font-medium">Body</span>
            <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight font-highlight">Where tension, stress, and imbalance accumulate.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="bg-tw-purple text-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] min-h-[320px] flex flex-col justify-between">
            <span class="text-tw-yellow uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-sm font-medium">Family</span>
            <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight font-highlight">Where patterns start, sometimes long before you.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="bg-tw-black text-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] min-h-[320px] flex flex-col justify-between">
            <span class="text-tw-yellow uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-sm font-medium">Work environment</span>
            <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight font-highlight">Where these patterns play out again and again.</p>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 max-w-4xl text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-tight font-highlight italic text-tw-black">
          You don’t need more coping strategies. You need to see and understand the systems you’re part of.
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-tw-yellow py-24 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-12">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-14 items-center">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="font-highlight text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-none tracking-tighter text-tw-black">
            You don’t become “perfect”.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-7 text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-snug font-light text-tw-black">
          <p>You become aware enough to stop repeating.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 font-medium">
            <li class="flex gap-4"><span>→</span><span>You recognize patterns before they trap you.</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-4"><span>→</span><span>You stop over-adapting to situations that drain you.</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-4"><span>→</span><span>You make decisions that actually align with you.</span></li>
          </ul>
          <p>Not because you forced yourself.</p>
          <p>Because the invisible chains that kept you trapped in your patterns have been brought to light and broken.</p>
          <p class="font-highlight italic text-4xl md:text-6xl leading-tight">And for the first time, your life really stops repeating itself.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-tw-black text-white py-24 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-12" id="contact">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mb-16">
          <p class="text-tw-yellow uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-sm font-medium mb-5">Beware</p>
          <h2 class="font-highlight text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-none tracking-tighter">
            This is not for everyone.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-14">
          <div class="border border-white/15 rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-10">
            <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-highlight mb-8 text-white/80">This is not for you if:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-5 text-xl md:text-2xl font-light text-white/70">
              <li>you want quick fixes</li>
              <li>you prefer staying comfortable in what you already know</li>
              <li>you’re not ready to question your own patterns</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white text-tw-black rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-10">
            <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-highlight mb-8">This is for you if:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-5 text-xl md:text-2xl font-light">
              <li>you’re tired of repeating the same story</li>
              <li>you’re ready to see what’s actually there, even if you don’t like it</li>
              <li>you want real change, not just insight</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/work-with-me" class="inline-flex bg-tw-yellow text-tw-black px-10 py-5 rounded-full items-center gap-3 text-lg hover:bg-white transition-colors group font-medium">
          Book Your Session
          <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-5 h-5 stroke-[1.5] group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
